name: Tucker Mcgrath
text: This place is the one I like best. I visit many restaurants but to this place I go the most. The team is very cordial and the cooking they cook is so good. I am always happy to have a good meal in this place. Highly recommended.

name: Alex Kohara
text: Quick and easy, freshly baked pizza. It's a good  deal at $9.85 for your own customized pizza at the airport.

name: Samuel Ross
text: VERY greasy and not very good. But it was fast and cheap

name: Rekha Subramanyan
text: Pizza was okay.  Customer service sucks.  Very stringent on potions.
